  lobInstructionsIntro: { eng: "Quick troubleshooting guide for common situations during your stay. Follow the steps calmly and contact INFTOUR if the issue persists.", esp: "Guía rápida para resolver situaciones habituales durante su estancia. Siga los pasos con calma y contacte con INFTOUR si el problema persiste.", ru: "Quick troubleshooting guide for common situations during your stay. Follow the steps calmly and contact INFTOUR if the issue persists.", fr: "Quick troubleshooting guide for common situations during your stay. Follow the steps calmly and contact INFTOUR if the issue persists.", it: "Quick troubleshooting guide for common situations during your stay. Follow the steps calmly and contact INFTOUR if the issue persists.", de: "Quick troubleshooting guide for common situations during your stay. Follow the steps calmly and contact INFTOUR if the issue persists.", uk: "Quick troubleshooting guide for common situations during your stay. Follow the steps calmly and contact INFTOUR if the issue persists.", pl: "Quick troubleshooting guide for common situations during your stay. Follow the steps calmly and contact INFTOUR if the issue persists." },
